column3: Ujin needs help if she is to do what the gods ask of her.
Survey the land for gaunt gedan.
Tell me, are you an experienced hunter?
I was told today that I need to go and clean the altar to the west. However, when I visited the area earlier, it was surrounded by beasts.
Please go to Chakha Zoh and slay any gaunt gedan you find. I cannot complete my duties without your help.
Please go to Chakha Zoh and slay any gaunt gedan you find.
You have already slayed the creatures? It seems I made the right decision asking you for help.
Thank you for everything, kind adventurer.
Please take this as a token of my thanks. I am currently training to be an udgan myself, though I am still lacking in experience. I look forward to the day when I am able to pray for you.
